{"tid":2149301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中方制裁11名美國人  港府：全力支持中央、配合執行","createTime":"2020-08-10T10:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T13:05:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a363b19009e4d81ddecb1789040043d68afc80","tid":2149301,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"美國財政部公佈制裁11名中港官員，包括行政長官林鄭月娥、港澳辦主任夏寶龍等人，中國外交部今日（10日）宣布，對11名美方人士實施制裁，包括美國參議員魯比奧、克魯茲。<br />\n<br />\n港府隨即發稿，稱全力支持中央政府對美方採取的反制措施，並會全面配合執行。新聞稿中，政府力斥美國政府日前變本加厲，針對中央人民政府及特區政府官員實施所謂「制裁」，行為卑劣及無恥，稱香港市民與全國人民一樣，無不感到憤慨。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/509170</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5987bb061b6e7360b390a7e01b2cb5c07a63a261","tid":2149301,"uid":38572,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:29:53.000Z","msg":"跟尾狗又係到叫"},{"pid":"8277d866910052a1a74f91acafe30b5fd99e8263","tid":2149301,"uid":15815,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"&quot;香港市民與全國人民一樣，無不感到憤慨。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa0fda08c4376f11cc9084e4cda5b9765676584","tid":2149301,"uid":271513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"而家應該連藍屍都當左港共無到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係人都知佢地而家連傀儡都唔係，只係啲行屍"},{"pid":"ff6b0c3ad67ba095d2cfcca70dedb012cd4167e9","tid":2149301,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:36:58.000Z","msg":"想知點配合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0958fdf241fe691188ec6e9992f19ccd9ca1747","tid":2149301,"uid":20222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:37:33.000Z","msg":"跟d 咩<br />\n唔俾人入我地依個第三世界國家?<br />\n係呀<br />\n恐怖份子做攻府既第三世界國家呀<img src=\"/asse